AiSummaryContaineruniface_104ocz1665702673286.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ocz1665702673286.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ocz1665702673286.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ocz1665702673286\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specifies the port number of the machine on which the Uniface Debugger process is\n      listening.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ocz1665702673286__topic_d145145e1_d145146e1_d145147e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ocz1665702673286__p_d145148e1_d145149e1_d145150e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">UDBG_Port</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">PortNumber</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"ocz1665702673286__section_w3153ab1b5b3_w3154ab1b5_w3155ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ocz1665702673286__p_d145151e1_d145152e1_d145153e1\">For example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">udbg_port=13005</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"ocz1665702673286__section_w3156ab1b5b5_w3157ab1b5_w3158ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ocz1665702673286__table_d17669e1_d17670e1_d17671e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">First available port number, starting with\n                        13001</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">File section: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"efz1665702672861.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/efz1665702672861.html\" title=\"The [install] section of the initialization file contains information about the current installation.\">[install]</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n